OL,3,CNew footage shows Tiger Woods' arrest
OL,4,Cafter rollover car crash
OL,6,FThe footage was released by Martin
OL,7,FCounty Sheriff's Office.
OL,9,FNewly released footage shows Tiger
OL,10,FWoods' arrest following his rollover
OL,11,Fcrash on Friday.
OL,13,FThe video shows Woods on one knee next
OL,14,Fto the road, not far from the car,
OL,15,Fwhich is still turned on its side
OL,16,Ffollowing the collision.
OL,18,FIn another part of the newly released
OL,19,Fvideo, Woods is shown submitting to a
OL,20,Ffield sobriety test, after which a
OL,21,Fdeputy places him in handcuffs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
