OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775199889
OL,3,CNew footage shows Tiger Woods' arrest
OL,4,Cafter rollover car crash
OL,6,F"At this time, I do believe your
OL,7,Fnormal faculties are impaired, okay?"
OL,8,Fthe deputy said. "And you're under an
OL,9,Funknown substance, okay, so at this
OL,10,Ftime you are under arrest for DUI."
OL,12,FWoods was charged with driving under
OL,13,Fthe influence, and released on bail in
OL,14,Fthe early hours of Saturday morning.
OL,16,FHe has pleaded not guilty, according
OL,17,Fto court documents and is scheduled to
OL,18,Fappear in court on 5 May.
