OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775199889
OL,3,CNew footage shows Tiger Woods' arrest
OL,4,Cafter rollover car crash
OL,6,FThe crash happened when he tried to
OL,7,Fovertake a truck pulling a trailer
OL,8,Fthat was slowing for a turn on a
OL,9,Fresidential street.
OL,11,FOfficers said he was driving at high
OL,12,Fspeed and clipped the trailer, causing
OL,13,Fhis Land Rover to roll over.
OL,15,FWhen officers arrived, he was found
OL,16,Fnear his car, uninjured.
OL,18,FHe told an officer he was checking his
OL,19,Fphone and tweaking the radio at the
OL,20,Ftime of the crash, and did not notice
OL,21,Fthe truck had slowed down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
