PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775199889
OL,3,CNew footage shows Tiger Woods' arrest
OL,4,Cafter rollover car crash
OL,6,FWhen he was taken to the police
OL,7,Fstation, he passed a breathalyser test
OL,8,Fbut refused to take a urine sample.
OL,10,FIn his first public comments since the
OL,11,Fincident, the US golf legend said he
OL,12,Fwould be stepping away from the sport,
OL,13,Fthat he "understands the seriousness
OL,14,Fof the situation", and he is now
OL,15,Flooking to "prioritise" his wellbeing.
OL,17,FThe 50-year-old had prescription
OL,18,Fpainkillers in his pocket and had been
OL,19,Flooking down at his phone before
OL,20,Fcrashing into another vehicle,
OL,21,Faccording to a sheriff's report.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
